WEBVTT

01:27.490 --> 01:31.850
[The Dark Romance]

01:32.259 --> 01:34.950
[Episode 8]

01:39.350 --> 01:41.610
How did Li Changning do in the follow-up?

01:42.400 --> 01:43.950
She's totally fine to go back to school.

01:43.950 --> 01:45.110
She's still sad,

01:45.479 --> 01:46.560
but Yuan Ye's ending

01:46.560 --> 01:48.120
is also a warning for her.

01:49.280 --> 01:51.940
Her desire to get back to normal
is stronger now.

01:53.350 --> 01:54.430
Thank you, Dr. Luo.

01:54.710 --> 01:55.640
You're welcome.

01:56.350 --> 01:56.950
I'm here.

01:58.509 --> 01:59.229
You live here?

01:59.229 --> 01:59.560
Yes.

02:04.680 --> 02:05.430
Usually,

02:06.120 --> 02:07.920
when movies get to this point,

02:08.960 --> 02:09.680
don't they always ask,

02:09.680 --> 02:11.540
"Want to come up for some coffee?"

02:12.080 --> 02:13.240
Coffee now?

02:14.000 --> 02:16.200
It's too late. We won't be able to sleep.

02:20.990 --> 02:22.070
You're so cute.

02:22.960 --> 02:24.050
Who asks for coffee

02:24.079 --> 02:25.280
at this hour?

02:25.440 --> 02:26.590
You definitely won't be able to sleep.

02:26.590 --> 02:26.990
Right.

02:27.910 --> 02:28.590
That's true.

02:28.590 --> 02:29.150
So,

02:29.750 --> 02:31.079
Jiale is at home, right?

02:32.870 --> 02:33.310
Yes.

02:34.310 --> 02:36.640
Then I definitely shouldn't go up, right?

02:36.680 --> 02:37.079
Otherwise,

02:37.079 --> 02:37.680
if he sees me,

02:37.680 --> 02:38.470
he might think

02:38.470 --> 02:40.530
I'm here to steal his little hamster.

02:41.750 --> 02:43.680
That hamster is his baby now.

02:44.190 --> 02:46.310
He won't even let me feed it.

02:46.310 --> 02:48.079
He's afraid I won't take good care of it

02:48.079 --> 02:49.750
and that it might escape.

02:52.030 --> 02:53.280
With such a responsible owner like him,

02:53.280 --> 02:54.210
I feel relieved.

02:54.630 --> 02:55.490
How about this?

02:55.800 --> 02:56.600
Ask him for me,

02:56.910 --> 02:57.910
when he is free,

02:58.430 --> 02:59.960
if he's willing to have a meal

02:59.960 --> 03:01.120
with a doctor like me.

03:01.120 --> 03:02.630
And then I'll tentatively ask him

03:02.630 --> 03:04.560
if he'd give the hamster back to me.

03:05.310 --> 03:05.840
Okay.

03:07.960 --> 03:09.020
I'll be going then.

03:10.560 --> 03:11.120
Ms. Yan.

03:15.800 --> 03:18.000
I saw a very different side of you today.

03:18.910 --> 03:20.170
A different side of me?

03:21.320 --> 03:23.650
When you were acting on the phone earlier,

03:25.310 --> 03:26.710
you looked very serious.

03:30.000 --> 03:30.750
That

03:31.590 --> 03:32.990
was my first time acting.

03:38.630 --> 03:40.200
The rain is getting heavier.

03:40.200 --> 03:41.560
You should head back now.

03:41.560 --> 03:41.910
Okay.

03:42.590 --> 03:43.079
See you.

03:54.480 --> 03:58.100
[Lihai Tattoo Forum]

03:59.360 --> 04:00.080
You

04:00.560 --> 04:01.560
seem very interested.

04:01.560 --> 04:02.420
Want to get one?

04:02.840 --> 04:04.040
You want me to get one?

04:04.840 --> 04:05.240
Why?

04:06.870 --> 04:09.130
How do you know about this tattoo design?

04:15.590 --> 04:17.000
You're very curious.

04:17.269 --> 04:18.160
Want to get one?

04:23.540 --> 04:26.880
[Lihai Tattoo Forum]

04:24.830 --> 04:25.900
Tell me first,

04:26.070 --> 04:27.830
where did you get that tattoo?

04:32.750 --> 04:34.510
That tiny tattoo is nothing.

04:35.310 --> 04:37.390
I've got way bigger ones on my body.

04:38.430 --> 04:39.560
You want to see them?

04:46.360 --> 04:47.620
It's me in the picture.

04:48.120 --> 04:48.780
Satisfied?

04:49.920 --> 04:53.510
I've never seen a woman like you.

04:54.040 --> 04:54.870
Let's exchange WeChat.

04:54.740 --> 04:57.320
[Eric]

05:09.800 --> 05:11.680
No phones while eating.

05:13.920 --> 05:15.180
I'm working.

05:23.140 --> 05:24.090
[Life is like a game]
[If you don't take risks]

05:24.120 --> 05:25.210
[How can you rise to the top?]

05:24.630 --> 05:25.360
Mom.

05:26.240 --> 05:27.700
You're acting a bit weird.

05:28.360 --> 05:29.290
What do you mean?

05:29.560 --> 05:31.070
You didn't use to

05:31.430 --> 05:33.030
look at your phone this much.

05:33.780 --> 05:35.020
Didn't I tell you?

05:35.120 --> 05:35.950
I'm working.

05:38.480 --> 05:39.480
Finish your food.

05:39.510 --> 05:40.480
We have to go.

05:40.480 --> 05:41.610
We're running late.

05:44.560 --> 05:46.310
I'm going to work out now.

05:46.480 --> 05:47.750
I've got a meeting later.

05:47.750 --> 05:48.960
What kind of meeting?

05:52.240 --> 05:54.600
Meetings won't stop me
from asking you out.

05:54.600 --> 05:56.320
-What do you do?
-Mom.

05:57.190 --> 05:57.750
Water.

06:00.540 --> 06:01.720
[Haha, it's a secret]

06:01.040 --> 06:01.740
It's a secret.

06:01.740 --> 06:02.800
[So mysterious]

06:01.800 --> 06:02.920
So mysterious.

06:03.000 --> 06:04.060
What are you doing?

06:04.800 --> 06:06.920
Don't tell me you're doing online dating.

06:06.920 --> 06:07.720
What are you talking about?

06:07.720 --> 06:08.600
I'm working.

06:08.720 --> 06:13.310
[But I really want to know.
Can you tell me?]

06:09.000 --> 06:10.480
Hurry. Go get your backpack.

06:10.480 --> 06:11.880
I'll be there in a minute.

06:12.510 --> 06:14.350
But I really want to know.

06:14.800 --> 06:15.930
Can you tell me?

06:16.870 --> 06:18.760
I gotta go, you vixen.

06:18.950 --> 06:20.150
Time to work out.

06:25.600 --> 06:27.600
Check out my recent workout results.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.000
Come and compete with me.

06:30.240 --> 06:31.390
Jiale, sit still.

06:31.390 --> 06:33.050
It's not safe to sit like that.

06:44.360 --> 06:44.870
Jiale.

06:45.560 --> 06:48.159
Do you know what GG means?

06:48.600 --> 06:49.240
Good game.

06:49.920 --> 06:51.720
Is it praising my gaming skills?

06:51.750 --> 06:53.270
It's sarcasm.

06:53.270 --> 06:55.240
I'm definitely GG for this exam,

06:55.240 --> 06:57.440
which means I'm definitely gonna fail.

06:59.040 --> 07:00.160
Why do you ask?

07:04.040 --> 07:05.040
I'm just curious.

07:18.190 --> 07:18.600
Bye.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.690
Pay attention in class.

07:24.680 --> 07:26.050
I'm done. Where are you?

07:26.190 --> 07:27.320
I can train with you.

07:28.040 --> 07:29.360
Why aren't you replying?

07:29.360 --> 07:30.120
GG.

07:30.310 --> 07:31.770
You're definitely GG now.

07:32.390 --> 07:33.310
I'm

07:33.480 --> 07:34.750
very good too.

07:35.560 --> 07:37.220
Do you want to train together?

07:37.480 --> 07:38.830
Let's have a match.

07:43.120 --> 07:45.120
I can't wait.

07:45.360 --> 07:47.820
Just thinking about you
in that tight outfit

07:48.360 --> 07:49.870
makes me drool.

07:51.560 --> 07:54.220
[International Medical Center]

07:54.390 --> 07:54.830
Here.

07:55.040 --> 07:55.720
Thank you, Dr. Luo.

07:55.720 --> 07:56.360
You're welcome.

07:56.360 --> 07:57.159
Take your medicine on time.

07:57.159 --> 07:57.510
Okay.

07:57.720 --> 07:58.530
Here, Dr. Luo.

08:00.560 --> 08:01.560
How many are left?

08:01.720 --> 08:02.690
Five or six left.

08:05.360 --> 08:11.050
[The famous doctors are here] [Luo Liang]

08:20.950 --> 08:22.350
You're recovering well.

08:22.950 --> 08:23.680
You can walk.

08:24.190 --> 08:26.430
Your appointments are really hard to get.

08:26.430 --> 08:27.630
If it weren't for the VIP clinic,

08:27.630 --> 08:29.090
I wouldn't have gotten in.

08:29.240 --> 08:30.720
I'm just here to see

08:31.750 --> 08:33.409
if the six hundred is worth it.

08:33.600 --> 08:34.530
What do you want?

08:35.960 --> 08:36.960
I just want to ask

08:38.030 --> 08:39.440
why every girl I meet

08:39.440 --> 08:40.549
loves me so much.

08:41.120 --> 08:41.870
When they hear the word "breakup,"

08:41.870 --> 08:43.360
they act like it's the end of the world.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.820
You've seen it too, right?

08:45.000 --> 08:46.270
What am I supposed to do

08:46.270 --> 08:48.600
to end things with them without any drama?

08:50.840 --> 08:52.700
You're seeing someone new again?

08:53.240 --> 08:55.510
A prodigal who returns
is worth more than gold.

08:55.510 --> 08:56.630
Why can't you just believe

08:56.630 --> 08:59.090
I actually want to be
in a real relationship?

09:02.790 --> 09:03.390
You

09:06.360 --> 09:07.910
are not looking for love.

09:08.630 --> 09:10.770
You're just trying to feel

09:10.870 --> 09:12.270
some sense of self-worth

09:15.360 --> 09:16.560
through those girls.

09:16.960 --> 09:18.790
You're trying to escape
the shadow of your father.

09:18.790 --> 09:20.650
Don't act like you know me so well.

09:28.000 --> 09:29.060
Making a clean exit

09:29.510 --> 09:31.370
means a quick, painless breakup.

09:32.150 --> 09:34.410
It means the girl is willing to walk away.

09:34.510 --> 09:35.770
She won't cling to you,

09:36.510 --> 09:37.870
and she might even be willing
to let you back in

09:37.870 --> 09:39.670
when you're feeling nostalgic.

09:40.030 --> 09:40.910
Am I right?

09:43.510 --> 09:44.550
Do you know how long I've searched

09:44.550 --> 09:46.610
to find this tiny bit of information?

09:50.910 --> 09:52.630
Dr. Luo seems to know more

09:52.950 --> 09:55.070
about how to train women than I do.

09:56.120 --> 09:57.180
For an independent

09:57.390 --> 09:58.940
and domineering woman

09:58.970 --> 10:00.520
like Ms. Yan,

10:02.250 --> 10:03.250
what would you do?

10:08.620 --> 10:10.080
You think too highly of me.

10:10.870 --> 10:12.370
But I have to remind you,

10:13.150 --> 10:15.610
your disrespectful attitude towards women

10:15.630 --> 10:16.290
is not okay.

10:17.170 --> 10:18.370
You need to change it.

10:21.320 --> 10:23.780
You'd better
take care of your injury first.

10:23.910 --> 10:25.310
Limping around like that

10:25.790 --> 10:26.790
is not cool at all.

10:28.360 --> 10:30.720
There's nothing wrong
with your mental state.

10:30.720 --> 10:31.960
You don't need my treatment

10:31.960 --> 10:32.840
or medicine.

10:34.000 --> 10:34.640
But

10:34.790 --> 10:37.050
I can still give you some medical advice.

10:37.270 --> 10:38.270
Balanced nutrition

10:38.270 --> 10:39.390
is especially important

10:39.390 --> 10:40.200
at your age.

10:40.600 --> 10:42.030
Don't be picky.

10:42.240 --> 10:43.720
Don't just eat one type of food.

10:43.720 --> 10:45.180
You need a variety of foods

10:45.550 --> 10:47.810
to support your growth and development.

10:48.240 --> 10:49.270
It'll help your brain

10:49.270 --> 10:50.240
work better too.

10:51.070 --> 10:54.070
[Lihai Renxin Hospital,
Initial Consultation Record]

11:04.630 --> 11:06.160
Do you need my help to get up?

11:35.750 --> 11:36.950
That girl,

11:37.750 --> 11:38.520
Yuan Ye,

11:40.030 --> 11:41.490
will she really go to jail?

11:44.150 --> 11:46.040
There is no final verdict yet.

11:46.670 --> 11:49.270
But Xu Feng has issued
a letter of forgiveness.

11:49.320 --> 11:51.580
So she'll likely get a lighter sentence.

11:52.720 --> 11:53.510
Feng.

11:53.670 --> 11:53.960
No,

11:55.360 --> 11:56.030
Xu Feng.

11:57.410 --> 11:59.040
He still likes her after all.

12:00.030 --> 12:01.400
You still miss him.

12:02.480 --> 12:03.090
Right?

12:16.200 --> 12:17.600
If you really miss him,

12:18.950 --> 12:20.250
write his name down.

12:25.480 --> 12:26.810
There was once someone

12:26.840 --> 12:27.390
I should have forgotten,

12:27.390 --> 12:28.440
but couldn't.

12:30.550 --> 12:31.840
At my worst,

12:32.360 --> 12:34.020
he was all I could think about.

12:34.750 --> 12:35.960
I couldn't do anything.

12:35.960 --> 12:37.490
I didn't want to see anyone.

12:37.990 --> 12:39.400
Later, I told myself

12:40.430 --> 12:42.520
to write his name down, and burn it.

12:43.630 --> 12:45.890
Once it's burned, he'll be out of my mind.

12:47.550 --> 12:48.550
Do you want to try?

13:04.510 --> 13:06.320
[Feng]

13:10.360 --> 13:14.760
[Feng]

13:24.510 --> 13:28.550
[Feng]

14:09.440 --> 14:11.120
I'm sorry, Ms. Yan.

14:11.440 --> 14:12.690
You can yell at me.

14:13.120 --> 14:14.830
I still miss him.

14:15.150 --> 14:17.250
I still miss him.

14:20.000 --> 14:21.720
Don't blame yourself, Changning.

14:21.720 --> 14:23.120
Love itself is not wrong.

14:24.120 --> 14:25.050
The only mistake

14:26.360 --> 14:27.430
is that we fell in love

14:27.430 --> 14:29.290
with someone who was not worth it.

14:29.320 --> 14:30.200
After this,

14:30.870 --> 14:32.220
will I really

14:32.510 --> 14:33.840
be able to forget him?

14:38.090 --> 14:39.280
[Feng]

14:38.440 --> 14:40.700
We wrote every single stroke ourselves.

14:42.390 --> 14:44.250
I believe we can definitely do it.

14:44.960 --> 14:46.160
We can erase them all.

14:49.750 --> 14:50.890
The wound might

14:51.360 --> 14:52.620
still hurt sometimes,

14:53.550 --> 14:56.010
but it won't tear you apart
the way it used to.

15:00.000 --> 15:01.000
It'll pass.

15:03.240 --> 15:04.510
It'll finally pass.

15:12.080 --> 15:13.340
Is everything packed?

15:21.320 --> 15:21.850
Let's go.

15:41.400 --> 15:42.800
Changning, you're back.

15:43.240 --> 15:44.120
Hello, Ms. Yan.

15:44.320 --> 15:45.180
Let me help you.

15:46.000 --> 15:47.480
This is the new bedsheet
Ms. Feng bought for you.

15:47.480 --> 15:48.120
Isn't it cute?

15:48.120 --> 15:49.380
It has puppy patterns.

15:50.240 --> 15:50.840
By the way,

15:51.030 --> 15:53.000
there's a new spicy hot pot place
in the cafeteria. It's really good.

15:53.000 --> 15:54.600
Ms. Yan, let's go eat there together.

15:54.600 --> 15:55.200
You guys go ahead.

15:55.200 --> 15:55.800
I'll pass.

15:56.240 --> 15:56.790
Okay.

15:56.960 --> 15:57.630
We'll head off then,

15:57.630 --> 15:58.200
Ms. Yan.

15:58.600 --> 15:59.440
Bye, Ms. Yan.

16:00.150 --> 16:01.000
Hurry, hurry.

16:01.390 --> 16:03.920
If we're late,
there won't be any shrimp left.

16:04.790 --> 16:05.440
Hey vixen,

16:05.020 --> 16:06.310
[Hey vixen, it's time for us to meet]

16:05.910 --> 16:07.600
it's time for us to meet.

16:06.340 --> 16:07.540
[Let's get to know each other deeper]

16:07.650 --> 16:09.980
[Wear something sexy]

16:08.080 --> 16:10.030
Let's get to know each other deeper.

16:10.030 --> 16:10.910
Tuesday night.

16:12.550 --> 16:13.880
I'll be waiting for you.

16:46.350 --> 16:49.780
[Welcome to Shuting Houseroom]

17:29.830 --> 17:30.400
Eric.

17:45.880 --> 17:47.740
Why did you pick a place like this?

17:48.350 --> 17:49.670
Just change...

17:50.070 --> 17:51.480
change things up a bit.

17:55.960 --> 17:57.390
You really like tattoos.

17:58.590 --> 17:59.560
You like

18:01.240 --> 18:02.510
the open-minded type?

18:04.000 --> 18:04.920
I...

18:04.920 --> 18:05.960
I... I...

18:06.400 --> 18:06.860
like...

18:07.640 --> 18:08.510
like them all.

18:10.960 --> 18:11.780
Do you know

18:11.800 --> 18:13.680
what that tattoo means?

18:14.440 --> 18:15.460
Who gave it to you?

18:16.680 --> 18:18.780
They all say it's the Eye of Medusa.

18:19.270 --> 18:20.510
Then how do you know

18:20.550 --> 18:22.880
those are octopus legs wrapped around it?

18:24.270 --> 18:26.200
I'll tell... tell...

18:27.000 --> 18:28.920
I'll tell you after we sleep.

18:29.310 --> 18:30.710
Who gave you that design?

18:31.240 --> 18:33.240
Why do you want me to get that tattoo?

18:34.110 --> 18:34.880
Don't rush.

18:34.960 --> 18:35.480
Take it off.

18:35.480 --> 18:36.350
Easy. Easy.

18:36.350 --> 18:37.010
Take it off.

18:37.030 --> 18:38.830
I'll tell you after you take it off.

18:38.830 --> 18:40.470
Don't rush, would you?

18:40.790 --> 18:42.280
You tell me first.

18:42.350 --> 18:43.280
Then take it off.

18:44.000 --> 18:45.270
Don't rush, I'll do it myself.

18:45.270 --> 18:46.600
I'll take it off myself.

18:48.640 --> 18:49.370
Tell me then.

18:52.080 --> 18:52.590
Tell me.

18:52.590 --> 18:53.920
Didn't you say you'd tell me?

18:53.920 --> 18:54.240
Wait a minute.

18:54.240 --> 18:55.720
Why aren't you keeping your word?

18:55.720 --> 18:56.480
I'll tell you after we sleep.

18:56.480 --> 18:57.480
-No, you tell me first.
-Let's sleep first.

18:57.480 --> 18:57.880
I'll tell you after we sleep.

18:57.880 --> 18:59.160
You tell me first!

18:59.160 --> 18:59.830
Don't move.

19:00.400 --> 19:01.070
You tell me first!

19:01.070 --> 19:02.530
After you tell me, I'll...

19:21.510 --> 19:21.960
Hello?

19:21.960 --> 19:23.000
What's wrong, son?

19:23.000 --> 19:24.600
You need to take me to school.

19:25.270 --> 19:26.670
Mom stayed out all night.

19:26.750 --> 19:28.210
She didn't come back home.

19:47.440 --> 19:48.370
Still no answer.

19:48.720 --> 19:50.290
What is Mom even busy with?

19:50.590 --> 19:52.640
Last night
she said she'd be out for a bit.

19:52.640 --> 19:54.640
Now she won't even pick up the phone.

19:57.000 --> 19:57.680
I think

19:57.680 --> 19:58.440
she just

19:58.590 --> 20:00.250
has something to do at school.

20:00.550 --> 20:01.550
Anyway,

20:01.920 --> 20:03.150
don't worry.

20:03.240 --> 20:04.770
Just focus on school, okay?

20:06.790 --> 20:07.680
She's an adult.

20:07.830 --> 20:08.950
She'll be fine.

20:09.400 --> 20:09.880
Okay?

20:10.830 --> 20:11.360
Go ahead.

20:13.510 --> 20:13.960
Bye.

20:16.310 --> 20:17.160
Bye.

20:20.280 --> 20:23.080
[Yan Ling, school]

20:23.170 --> 20:26.330
[Lihai, Unknown Caller]

20:26.590 --> 20:27.010
Hello?

20:28.680 --> 20:29.280
This is he.

20:32.720 --> 20:33.070
Po...

20:33.960 --> 20:35.160
Police station?

20:46.030 --> 20:47.750
You need to improve
your safety awareness from now on.

20:47.750 --> 20:49.200
This kind of misunderstanding
can't happen again.

20:49.200 --> 20:50.270
And you're a college teacher.

20:50.270 --> 20:51.600
Check your belongings.

20:52.000 --> 20:53.800
Sign here if there's no problem.

21:01.110 --> 21:02.310
Pack up and you can go.

21:12.700 --> 21:14.510
[Cheng'an Branch,
Lihai Public Security Bureau]

21:14.540 --> 21:16.420
[Nanchangdian Police Station]

21:16.720 --> 21:17.590
What's the situation?

21:17.590 --> 21:19.250
Why are you dressed like this?

21:21.830 --> 21:22.550
I can't believe it.

21:22.550 --> 21:23.610
You know, just now,

21:23.640 --> 21:24.960
when I got the call
saying you were at the police station,

21:24.960 --> 21:26.620
I was like, "What's going on?"

21:27.070 --> 21:28.310
You stayed out all night

21:28.310 --> 21:29.440
and left your kid at home

21:29.440 --> 21:30.700
just to go out on a date.

21:31.550 --> 21:36.880
[Police]

21:31.880 --> 21:32.680
What nonsense are you talking about?

