37:29.110 --> 37:30.070
associating something

37:30.070 --> 37:32.280
with the feeling

37:32.280 --> 37:33.740
of excitement and shyness.

37:33.740 --> 37:38.030
[Kino] [NLP]

37:33.920 --> 37:35.110
The anchor you use

37:35.440 --> 37:38.000
